            {
                "comment": "First half of the class was very interesting, but after the first midterm it got boring. He tried to make it entertaining and was good at explaining very dry material. Exams were fair, very long, but definitely based on the homework and lectures. Do the homework and understand it, go to office hours, they'll help a lot.",
                "difficulty_rating": 4,
                "quality_rating": 4
